The Moonwell Card is a crypto debit card designed to bring the power of onchain finance into everyday transactions. Built on the Moonwell protocol—a user-friendly lending and borrowing platform operating on Base and Optimism—it enables users to load funds using USDC, either directly from their wallet or by borrowing against assets supplied on Moonwell. With no annual fees, support for Apple Pay and Google Pay, automated reloads, and smart spending controls, the Moonwell Card combines convenience, security, and flexibility.

